title: Thousands flock to vehicle auction of Saudi tycoon
text:
Thousands flock to vehicle auction of Saudi tycoon 1:44pm EDT - 01:17 
Hundreds of vehicles are sold at an auction in Saudi Arabia to settle the debt of billionaire Maan al-Sanea and his company, one of the kingdom's longest-running debt disputes.
